            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Fabricius <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ouf</abbr><ex>entia</ex></expan> Pri<lb break="no" n="2"/>mus Como miles <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XI <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>laudiae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr><am><g type="centuria"/></am></abbr><ex>centuria</ex></expan> Gemini <lb n="4"/>Flavi <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XX <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> XXXVIII <expan><abbr>testame</abbr><ex>nto</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ieri</ex></expan> iussit <expan><abbr>her</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>faciundum curavit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: nicht vor 42. n. Chr., als die legio XI die Beinamen Claudia pia fidelis erhielt; sie war bis 69 n. Chr. in Burnum stationiert. Verknüpfung mit Lupa 23087 vorbehaltlich einer Überprüfung durch A. Kurilić, 6.11.2014).</p>
            </div>
